AIM Assault SO

Combat map, styled assault garage at night, possible csgo port.
Probably my first aim_maps map, I started making it with the intention of being a 1 vs 1 map, but I think I will bring this idea to csgo.

- M4 and usp VS AK and glock ( you automatically take the weapons )
- 18 Slots ( 9 vs 9 )
- 2 Scouts
